{
  "texts": [
    "The estimations relate the real-time position of the sensor in the EM frame (Ψ EM) to the target frame (Ψ T).",
    "(b) The source side contains the haptic device controlled by the user to move the robotic arm.",
    "The user moves the handle in the yo direction relative to the initial location of frame (Ψ O).",
    "(c) The replica side contains the liver phantom with a spherical lead target located inside the phantom.",
    "The EM tracker system is attached to the phantom and used as a surrogate signal, and the C-arm scan is used to train and validate our methods."
  ]
}